POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 56.51% to NT$173,771,000 from NT$399,550,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            173,771          399,550    
YOY%             -56.51%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            590,442         1,817,948   
YOY%             -67.52% 
=================================================================
 